2>Water Pump
Fixed Charges 95 (1.5 HP power Line)

## Power Slabs used as on Date 1st-June-2020 is
upto 30 units 3.75rs
30-100 units 5.2rs
>100 units 6.75rs

## Taxes @ 4% of units Consumed

